Public MustOverride Function TypeAt(index As Integer?) As String

children.summary: Gets the full name of the type of the element at the given index, if known. Since this uses the item cache produced by enumeration, it may return null when we haven't enumerated enough to see the given element, or if we enumerated so much that the item has left the cache, or if the item at the given index is null. It will also return null when the index is null.
